Package: miraculix
Version: 0.9.0
Title: Algebraic and Statistical Functions for Genetics
Author: Malena Erbe [aut, cre], Martin Schlather [aut, cre], Florian Skene [aut], Alexander Freudenberg [ctr]
Description: This is a collection of fast tools based on SIMD and OMP needed in genetics, for instance, the calculation of the genetic relationship matrix. In particular, it is used in the breeding planning programme MoBPS at <https://github.com/tpook92/MoBPS>. It also contains the scanning approach by Kabluchko and Spodarev (2009), <doi:10.1239/aap/1240319575>.
Maintainer: Martin Schlather <schlather@math.uni-mannheim.de>
LinkingTo: RandomFieldsUtils
Depends: R (>= 3.0), RandomFieldsUtils (>= 0.5.3)
Imports: methods, graphics
Suggests:
License: GPL ( >= 3)
Biarch: true
URL: http://ms.math.uni-mannheim.de/de/publications/software/miraculix
NeedsCompilation: yes
Packaged: 2019-07-24 09:18:24 UTC; schlather
